# R8 keep rules for the instrumented-test (androidTest) APK.
# AGP combines all keep rule files in src/androidTest/keepRules to pass to R8.

# Native-lib SDKs (e.g. com.tencent:mmkv) carry errorprone annotations that
# reference compile-only JDK classes absent at runtime. The test APK shrinks with
# R8 too, so it needs the same suppression.
-dontwarn javax.lang.model.element.Modifier
